<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 15:12:42 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国弃权后联合国安理会要求加沙立即停火</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/un-security-council-demands-immediate-ceasefire-gaza-2024-03-25/</link><description>联合国安理会周一要求以色列和巴勒斯坦武装分子哈马斯立即停火，并在美国投弃权票后立即无条件释放所有人质。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 14:43:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/un-security-council-demands-immediate-ceasefire-gaza-2024-03-25/</guid></item><item><title>德国工业界对中国平等对待外国公司的承诺持怀疑态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/german-industry-sceptical-chinas-vow-treat-foreign-firms-equally-2024-03-25/</link><description>北京方面新承诺将外国公司视为国内竞争对手，但遭到其最大贸易伙伴之一德国的冷淡回应，德国各行业呼吁采取具体行动而不是空谈来创造一个真正的公平竞争环境。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 14:01:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/german-industry-sceptical-chinas-vow-treat-foreign-firms-equally-2024-03-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国国务院总理刘建超将于3月25日至28日访问新加坡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-liu-jianchao-visit-singapore-march-25-28-2024-03-25/</link><description>新加坡外交部周一晚间发表声明称，应新加坡外交部长维文的邀请，中共中央对外联络部部长刘建超将于3月25日至28日访问新加坡。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 13:25:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-liu-jianchao-visit-singapore-march-25-28-2024-03-25/</guid></item><item><title>佳士得将在香港开设新总部，亚洲 Z 世代兴趣日益浓厚</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/christies-open-new-hong-kong-hq-sees-growing-asian-gen-z-interest-2024-03-25/</link><description>佳士得拍卖行希望其 9 月在香港开设的占地 50,000 平方英尺的亚洲新总部能够在 2024 年提高销售额，因为该地区新一代文化敏锐的千禧一代和年轻人的兴趣日益浓厚。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 11:46:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/christies-open-new-hong-kong-hq-sees-growing-asian-gen-z-interest-2024-03-25/</guid></item><item><title>韩国足球运动员孙俊浩被中国释放</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/south-korean-soccer-player-son-jun-ho-has-been-released-by-china-yonhap-2024-03-25/</link><description>韩国外交部周一表示，自 2023 年 5 月以来一直被中国拘留的韩国足球运动员孙俊浩最近已被释放并回国。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 11:26:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/south-korean-soccer-player-son-jun-ho-has-been-released-by-china-yonhap-2024-03-25/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国敦促银行加快批准私人开发商的新贷款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-pushes-banks-speed-approvals-new-loans-private-developers-say-sources-2024-03-25/</link><description>知情人士表示，中国监管机构正在敦促银行加快审批向现金匮乏的私人房地产开发商发放的新贷款，此举旨在重振购房者的信心，而购房者的情绪可能会削弱贷款机构的资产质量。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 11:06:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-pushes-banks-speed-approvals-new-loans-private-developers-say-sources-2024-03-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国外交部副部长称中菲关系正处于十字路口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-vice-foreign-minister-says-relations-with-philippines-are-crossroads-2024-03-25/</link><description>中国外交部副部长陈晓东表示，当前中菲关系正处于十字路口，菲方必须谨慎行事。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 10:56:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-vice-foreign-minister-says-relations-with-philippines-are-crossroads-2024-03-25/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：随着季度末的临近，日本和中国抑制降压</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-25/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 10:02:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-25/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜高级官员在北京会见中国国家主席王毅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/senior-north-korean-official-meets-chinas-wang-yi-beijing-2024-03-25/</link><description>官方媒体朝中社周一称，朝鲜高级官员率领代表团访问中国，周六会见了中国外交部长王毅，并呼吁加强两个邻国之间的关系。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 09:07:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/senior-north-korean-official-meets-chinas-wang-yi-beijing-2024-03-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车制造商在曼谷车展上成为焦点，推出新车型</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-makers-take-centre-stage-bangkok-motor-show-unveil-new-models-2024-03-25/</link><description>受强劲电动汽车销量的推动，中国汽车制造商将在本周的曼谷国际汽车展上成为众人瞩目的焦点，突显出长期主导泰国汽车市场的日本汽车巨头面临的日益严峻的挑战。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 07:13:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-makers-take-centre-stage-bangkok-motor-show-unveil-new-models-2024-03-25/</guid></item><item><title>日产计划到 2027 年推出 30 款新车型，提升全球销量</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nissan-targets-1-mln-vehicle-sales-growth-over-next-three-years-2024-03-25/</link><description>日产汽车周一表示，将在未来三年内推出 30 款新车型，目标是将全球销量增加 100 万辆，同时削减成本以提高盈利能力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 06:26:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nissan-targets-1-mln-vehicle-sales-growth-over-next-three-years-2024-03-25/</guid></item><item><title>数据显示，亚洲私募股权交易第一季度将创 2015 年以来最差水平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/asia-private-equity-deals-set-worst-q1-since-2015-data-shows-2024-03-25/</link><description>数据显示，由于中国交易停滞以及更广泛的经济和地缘政治不确定性拖累市场情绪，亚洲私募股权支持的并购活动将迎来近十年来最糟糕的开局。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 05:02:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/asia-private-equity-deals-set-worst-q1-since-2015-data-shows-2024-03-25/</guid></item><item><title>新交所将披露第三季度大宗商品交易商头寸</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/sgx-disclose-trader-positions-commodities-q3-2024-03-25/</link><description>新交所集团计划从第三季度开始每周披露铁矿石、橡胶和货运等大宗商品的交易头寸，以随着更多亚洲以外的交易商参与市场而提高透明度。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 04:52:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/sgx-disclose-trader-positions-commodities-q3-2024-03-25/</guid></item><item><title>小米首席执行官调侃即将推出的汽车的价格，展厅开始展示车辆</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/xiaomi-car-app-launched-apples-app-store-china-2024-03-25/</link><description>小米首席执行官周一表示，该公司的首款电动汽车旨在成为价格低于 50 万元（69,424 美元）的“最漂亮、最容易驾驶和最智能的汽车”，这家中国电子制造商本周正在准备接受订单。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 04:17:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/xiaomi-car-app-launched-apples-app-store-china-2024-03-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国誓言在产业升级过程中平等对待外国企业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-safeguard-national-treatment-foreign-funded-firms-2024-03-25/</link><description>随着亚洲最大经济体升级和强化产业链，中国周一承诺将给予外国企业与国内企业同等的待遇，以吸引更多的外国投资、合作和专业知识。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 01:34:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-safeguard-national-treatment-foreign-funded-firms-2024-03-25/</guid></item></channel></rss>